query:
-- Verificar registros em testResults
SELECT 
  tr.id,
  tr.invitationId,
  tr.employeeId,
  e.name as employeeName,
  e.employeeCode,
  tr.testType,
  tr.profileType,
  tr.completedAt,
  tr.createdAt
FROM testResults tr
LEFT JOIN employees e ON tr.employeeId = e.id
ORDER BY tr.completedAt DESC
LIMIT 50;
